OL,3,CWill there be a hosepipe ban in the UK?
OL,5,FIt's been a remarkably dry few weeks -
OL,6,Fif not months. It's looking to be one
OL,7,Fof the driest springs on record, with
OL,8,Frainfall well below average everywhere.
OL,10,FNationally, last autumn and winter saw
OL,11,Faverage rainfall levels, which have
OL,12,Fhelped to maintain reservoir and
OL,13,Fgroundwater supplies across the
OL,14,Fcountry.
