OL,3,CWill there be a hosepipe ban in the UK?
OL,5,FThe Environment Agency (EA) is closely
OL,6,Fmonitoring water companies'
OL,7,Fimplementation of dry weather plans,
OL,8,Fespecially in high-risk locations, and
OL,9,Fis preparing advice and information
OL,10,Ffor the public, including small steps
OL,11,Fthey can take to reduce usage.
OL,13,FAmong the possible options on the
OL,14,Ftable for water companies is a
OL,15,Fhosepipe ban, but what needs to happen
OL,16,Ffor this to be introduced, and how
OL,17,Flong will it last?
