OL,3,CWill there be a hosepipe ban in the UK?
OL,5,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,6,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,7,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,8,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,10,FWhat needs to happen for a hosepipe
OL,11,Fban to be put in place?
OL,13,FA hosepipe ban, officially called a
OL,14,FTemporary Use Ban (TUB), can be
OL,15,Fintroduced by a water company when
OL,16,Fsupplies come under pressure, usually
OL,17,Fdue to prolonged dry weather.
