OL,3,CWill there be a hosepipe ban in the UK?
OL,5,FAlthough the EA monitors drought
OL,6,Fconditions, it's the individual water
OL,7,Fcompanies who make the decision when
OL,8,Fit comes to a hosepipe ban.
OL,10,FTypically, a ban may be considered
OL,11,Fwhen rainfall has been well below
OL,12,Faverage for several weeks or months,
OL,13,Fwhen reservoir and groundwater levels
OL,14,Fare lower than normal for the time of
OL,15,Fyear or when there's a higher demand
OL,16,Fdue to hot weather.
