OL,3,CWill there be a hosepipe ban in the UK?
OL,5,F"It's been the driest early spring
OL,6,Fsince 1956 across England. Reservoirs
OL,7,Fare 84% full and there is now a
OL,8,Fmedium, but increasing, risk of
OL,9,Fdrought," the EA has warned.
OL,11,F"There are currently no plans for
OL,12,Fhosepipe bans. If the prolonged dry
OL,13,Fweather continues, water companies may
OL,14,Fneed to implement their dry weather
OL,15,Fplans in the weeks and months ahead."
OL,17,FWhat happens if it is brought into
OL,18,Fplace?
