OL,3,CWill there be a hosepipe ban in the UK?
OL,5,FIf a ban is announced, households are
OL,6,Flegally restricted from using
OL,7,Fhosepipes for a range of non-essential
OL,8,Factivities such as watering gardens or
OL,9,Flawns, washing cars or filling
OL,10,Fpaddling or swimming pools, cleaning
OL,11,Fpatios or windows with a hose.
OL,13,FBreaching the rules can lead to fines
OL,14,Fof up to #1,000.
OL,16,FHow long could it last?
