OL,3,CWill there be a hosepipe ban in the UK?
OL,5,FThe length of a hosepipe ban depends
OL,6,Fon weather conditions and how quickly
OL,7,Fwater sources recover. In past years,
OL,8,Fbans have lasted from a few weeks to
OL,9,Fseveral months.
OL,11,FIn 2022, when we experienced three
OL,12,Fheatwaves in as many months and
OL,13,Ftemperatures exceeded 40C, a ban was
OL,14,Fintroduced across parts of southern
OL,15,FEngland and remained in place through
OL,16,Fthe autumn after one of the driest
OL,17,Fsummers on record.
OL,19,FCould one be on the way this year?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
