OL,3,CWill there be a hosepipe ban in the UK?
OL,5,FIt remains to be seen. Much depends on
OL,6,Fthe next few weeks.
OL,8,FCurrently, some rain is forecast in
OL,9,Fplaces through this Bank Holiday
OL,10,Fweekend, with a signal for an
OL,11,Fimprovement as we go into the first
OL,12,Fcouple of weeks of June.
